title: march 15: teenagers strike back
description:
In this episode of 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about the student climate strikes led by Swedish teenager Greta Thunberg. After, she looks back at Justin Timberlake’s third album, The 20/20 Experience. Listen to this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
